      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump under identical geometric and fluid conditions as the COU. The five operating points span the clinical CPB flow-speed envelope. Minor differences in inlet turbulence intensity between the experimental and CFD setups were assessed and found to have negligible impact on hemolysis index predictions."
    },
    {
